{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Scrap Collector</u> is a game where you stack cards to craft new items, make new buildings, and fight the enemies. An example is if you have a &quot;Bot&quot; and place it on to a &quot;Scrap Pile&quot;, it will spawn material cards that you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/Basic_GameplayGif.gif?t=1738809114\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Explore</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> &quot;Explore&quot; cards allow you to search an area for resources, enemies, or even random encounters! Be careful as somethings are better left unfound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/ExplorationGif.gif?t=1738809114\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Combat</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Placing the player or a bot card on an enemy will engage in automatic combat. Fight bugs, hostile people and many other things. You can improve your odds of winning combat by teaming bots up against enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/extras/Combat.gif?t=1738809114\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Researching and Leveling</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You unlock new blueprints by leveling up. Every action the player performs adds exp.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738809114","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/page.bg.jpg?t=1738809114","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738809114","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps